message.text:
🚨 FINAL CALL! 🚨
This is your LAST CHANCE to join the Far Eastern University Chorale!

Auditions close on September 24, 2025 — once it’s over, it’s over. Don’t miss the opportunity to be part of FEU’s premier choir, a family that has raised Tamaraw pride on national and international stages. 🌍✨

📅 September 22–24, 2025
⏰ 4:00 PM – 6:00 PM
📍 FEU Center for the Arts, Ground Floor, Engineering Building, FEU Manila

If you’ve been waiting for a sign — this is it. 🚨 Walk-ins are welcome, but time is running out. Step up, sing out, and make your voice heard. 🎶

⏳ The stage won’t wait forever. Audition NOW!

#FEUChorale #FEU #KanTamaraw #LastChance #Auditions #FEUChoraleAuditions #JoinUs #TamarawPride

message.text:
🚨 FINAL CALL! 🚨
This is your LAST CHANCE to join the Far Eastern University Chorale!

Auditions close on September 24, 2025 — once it’s over, it’s over. Don’t miss the opportunity to be part of FEU’s premier choir, a family that has raised Tamaraw pride on national and international stages. 🌍✨

📅 September 22–24, 2025
⏰ 4:00 PM – 6:00 PM
📍 FEU Center for the Arts, Ground Floor, Engineering Building, FEU Manila

If you’ve been waiting for a sign — this is it. 🚨 Walk-ins are welcome, but time is running out. Step up, sing out, and make your voice heard. 🎶

⏳ The stage won’t wait forever. Audition NOW!

#FEUChorale #FEU #KanTamaraw #LastChance #Auditions #FEUChoraleAuditions #JoinUs #TamarawPride

message.text:
[Groovers ‘25-‘26: TamHunt 2025 Membership Applications]

📢 𝗖𝗔𝗟𝗟𝗜𝗡𝗚 𝗔𝗟𝗟 𝗔𝗦𝗣𝗜𝗥𝗔𝗡𝗧𝗦! 📢

Ready to step up, show up, and stand out? Whether you perform on stage, capture stories through media, or create designs that inspire — this is your moment to join the movement.

𝐅𝐨𝐫 𝐀𝐮𝐝𝐢𝐭𝐢𝐨𝐧𝐞𝐞𝐬 (𝐏𝐞𝐫𝐟𝐨𝐫𝐦𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐌𝐞𝐦𝐛𝐞𝐫𝐬): 
🗓 September 15–17 | ⏰ 6:00–8:30 PM

𝐅𝐨𝐫 𝐀𝐩𝐩𝐥𝐢𝐜𝐚𝐧𝐭𝐬 (𝐍𝐨𝐧-𝐏𝐞𝐫𝐟𝐨𝐫𝐦𝐢𝐧𝐠 𝐌𝐞𝐦𝐛𝐞𝐫𝐬):
🗓 September 10-16 | ⏰ Forms open until 11:59 PM

Click the link below to register:
https://bit.ly/ITHMGrooversMembershipApplications2025

📌 Stay tuned for the official guidelines and instructions. Keep your eyes open — 𝘵𝘩𝘦 𝘤𝘢𝘭𝘭 𝘥𝘳𝘰𝘱𝘴 𝘴𝘰𝘰𝘯.

Pubmat by: 
Hisami Muramatsu 
Deanne Jacqueline Paciente 

Caption by: Hisami Muramatsu 

#TamHunt2025
#MembershipApplications2025 
#AfterGround
#ITHMGroovers

message.text:
𝐇𝐨𝐫𝐧𝐬 𝐔𝐩, 𝐏𝐀𝐓𝐀𝐦𝐬!

It's that time of the year again! Be ready to put your game faces on as the 𝗜𝗧𝗛𝗠 𝗦𝗽𝗼𝗿𝘁𝘀𝗳𝗲𝘀𝘁 𝘁𝗿𝘆-𝗼𝘂𝘁𝘀 are bound to begin! Whether you're a returning athlete or trying something new, this is your chance to rise, represent, and showcase your grit in this year's most anticipated event!

🗓️: 𝗦𝗲𝗽𝘁𝗲𝗺𝗯𝗲𝗿 𝟮𝟬, 𝟮𝟬𝟮𝟱 (𝗦𝗮𝘁𝘂𝗿𝗱𝗮𝘆)
⏰: 𝟲:𝟯𝟬 𝗣𝗠 - 𝟴:𝟯𝟬 𝗣𝗠
📍: 𝗙𝗘𝗨 𝗖𝗼𝘂𝗿𝘁

Now is the time to show us what you've got! Push your limits, rise to the challenge and earn your spot, PATAms! 

Caption by: Jea Madronio
Pubmat by: Vince Maligang

𝐇𝐨𝐫𝐧𝐬 𝐔𝐩, 𝐏𝐀𝐓𝐀𝐦𝐬!

It's that time of the year again! Be ready to put your game faces on as the 𝗜𝗧𝗛𝗠 𝗦𝗽𝗼𝗿𝘁𝘀𝗳𝗲𝘀𝘁 𝘁𝗿𝘆-𝗼𝘂𝘁𝘀 are bound to begin! Whether you're a returning athlete or trying something new, this is your chance to rise, represent, and showcase your grit in this year's most anticipated event!

🗓️: 𝗦𝗲𝗽𝘁𝗲𝗺𝗯𝗲𝗿 𝟮𝟬, 𝟮𝟬𝟮𝟱 (𝗦𝗮𝘁𝘂𝗿𝗱𝗮𝘆)
⏰: 𝟲:𝟯𝟬 𝗣𝗠 - 𝟴:𝟯𝟬 𝗣𝗠
📍: 𝗙𝗘𝗨 𝗖𝗼𝘂𝗿𝘁

Now is the time to show us what you've got! Push your limits, rise to the challenge and earn your spot, PATAms! 

Caption by: Jea Madronio
Pubmat by: Vince Maligang

#PATAPHFEU
